WEBVTT

00:00:22.363 --> 00:00:26.075
debaa iyo muziniyo wa watruwashe
ilo dangandzo la dini wa watruwashe

00:00:27.335 --> 00:00:33.404
watru uzina kulatsa awo wakati ta wakati

00:00:33.576 --> 00:00:35.716
watru wuvumbwa dzina la Mungu

00:00:35.997 --> 00:00:38.068
tsena na dzina la mutrume Mohamed

00:00:38.278 --> 00:00:41.995
na masuhaba yahe
na udjama wahe

00:00:42.169 --> 00:00:43.932
na trongo ndri

00:00:44.133 --> 00:00:45.974
rendré harmwa tsi nyengi

00:00:46.146 --> 00:00:48.638
harmwa hafla za twarika

00:00:48.700 --> 00:00:50.614
mufano bara la hindi

00:00:50.678 --> 00:00:52.928
Ngudja, Copenhage

00:00:53.006 --> 00:00:55.506
Suyed na Turki

00:00:55.560 --> 00:00:58.092
London, tsena na Ulaya

00:00:58.193 --> 00:01:00.974
wami hedza debaa rangu nakana maha shendra

00:01:01.123 --> 00:01:03.060
wakatiyo debaa lika la watru baba

00:01:03.099 --> 00:01:04.724
lako hedzewa na watrubaba

00:01:04.857 --> 00:01:07.185
waja wasomedza watruwashe

00:01:07.279 --> 00:01:09.467
riyendresa li debaa ata leo

00:01:13.958 --> 00:01:18.004
mubadziyo wuwo mtrungiyo

00:01:18.536 --> 00:01:19.575
na mafikira

00:01:19.692 --> 00:01:22.060
ramoka mitwalaani

00:01:22.428 --> 00:01:26.263
mutru wabiya wanahe y tsi para kada,
nari ungaliye neka istawi

00:01:26.381 --> 00:01:29.427
sayile watru piya wuyidjerebu wu yi djerebu

00:01:29.787 --> 00:01:32.130
wu yistawidza

00:01:32.185 --> 00:01:34.232
wasi yi linganitsa ile paré istawi

00:01:34.287 --> 00:01:36.333
rijiviwe piyasi tsena rikaliye radi

00:01:44.217 --> 00:01:46.420
wasi usomedza wanatsa na uwa fundrisa

00:01:46.483 --> 00:01:48.357
ile waje warendze li bandza

00:01:48.513 --> 00:01:51.380
lilo djimbo bvolebvole

00:01:52.349 --> 00:01:54.404
twarika ya taswawufi

00:01:55.224 --> 00:01:57.317
bayna ya watruwashe

00:01:57.497 --> 00:01:59.699
uwo tsi mbadzio wa watrubaba

00:02:01.411 --> 00:02:04.777
bva ma djini wa bvendzawo debaa

00:02:05.115 --> 00:02:08.177
bva ma djini wa bvedzao trongo 
za sharabu na wusilamu

00:02:08.224 --> 00:02:09.966
yawo ma islamu

00:02:10.926 --> 00:02:13.747
yamo kiya debaa

00:02:13.966 --> 00:02:17.162
yawo wujo ngandza na wubadza debaa na wasi

00:02:17.396 --> 00:02:21.028
djini iyo pebvo awo mushibihi wayo

00:02:21.599 --> 00:02:24.919
moni nayi kuruani isrongowa 
awba wawo watru mori de wasi

00:02:25.051 --> 00:02:26.293
be wasi kari wa wono

00:02:26.435 --> 00:02:28.146
wilo wu ka shitswani paka mutru afe

00:02:28.302 --> 00:02:30.364
baanda mutru afa wilo wutrala

00:02:30.435 --> 00:02:33.536
lendre ha mutru wangina, wilo kalifu

00:02:33.568 --> 00:02:34.841
djini kalifu

00:02:35.068 --> 00:02:36.896
bva wema bva wayi

00:02:46.193 --> 00:02:47.943
nitso bvendza tsi latsa ji

00:02:48.303 --> 00:02:52.349
watru warenge mhono mili anda zatru

00:02:52.888 --> 00:02:54.583
utamaduni watru

00:02:54.935 --> 00:02:56.529
rizi hudze

00:02:56.787 --> 00:02:58.310
rizi hifadhwi

00:02:58.654 --> 00:03:00.958
rizibve bandza

00:03:01.709 --> 00:03:05.536
maana kula tsi kayina anda 
na mila na wutamaduni

00:03:05.756 --> 00:03:08.560
kayna hayiri

00:03:08.709 --> 00:03:11.451
mawuri mutru kana koho

00:03:11.521 --> 00:03:14.099
nisu hedza ji tsena

00:03:14.217 --> 00:03:17.295
na risike mihono mili wutamaduni 
watru na zi anda na mila